# Assets Intangible Finite Life Excluding Goodwill Gross Amount

## identifier
de8775

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of intangible assets held by the reporting party as at the relevant date, gross of any provision for impairment, and which are deemed to have a finite life. The measurement and classification basis used is to be in accordance with the accounting standards. 

For the purposes of this item exclude goodwill.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Intangible.FiniteLifeExcludingGoodwillGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo7.02.06
- period=instant
